title: Amy and Eddie Compete For The Morning Corny + Highlights From Bobby’s Pool Party

description:
The show shares their highlights from Bobby’s Memorial Day pool party at his new house. We get an update on “Gladys” – Amy’s son’s potentially make-believe girlfriend. Also, Amy and Eddie compete at The Morning Corny!
